<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
Schema: specification_document_mim
<express_ref linkend="specification_document:mim:specification_document_mim"/>
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="specification_document_mim">
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
Entity: document_identifier
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Specification_document_mim.document_identifier">
A <b>document_identifier</b> is a type of <express_ref linkend="group_schema:ir_express:group_schema.group"/> that specifies an identifier qualified by a name for a document.
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
WR: document_identifier.WR1
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Specification_document_mim.document_identifier.wr:WR1">
A <b>document_identifier</b> shall be referenced at least once by a  <express_ref linkend="Specification_document:mim:Specification_document_mim.document_identifier_assignment"/>.
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
UR: document_identifier.UR1
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Specification_document_mim.document_identifier.ur:UR1">
The combination of name and description inherited from group shall be unique.
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
Entity: document_identifier_assignment
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Specification_document_mim.document_identifier_assignment"><p>
A <b>document_identifier_assignment</b> is a type of <express_ref linkend="management_resources_schema:ir_express:management_resources_schema.group_assignment"/> that specifies one or more of  <express_ref linkend="Specification_document:mim:Specification_document_mim.document_identifier_assigned_item"/>.  If there are more than one, then the <b>items</b> are all revisions of the same drawing.
</p><example>
A schematic diagram may have a base identifier and each revision identification of that diagram differs from other revisions identification only in the document.description.
</example>
<note>
Due to a constraint on  <express_ref linkend="Specification_document:mim:Specification_document_mim.document_identifier"/>, no member of  <express_ref linkend="Specification_document:mim:Specification_document_mim.document_identifier"/> may be referenced more than once, guaranteeing uniqueness of <b>assigned_group</b>.
</note>
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
Attribute: document_identifier_assignment.items
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Specification_document_mim.document_identifier_assignment.items">
<p>
specifies a role of the <express_ref linkend="specification_document:mim:Specification_document_mim.document_identifier_assigned_item"/> for the <b>document_identifier_assignment</b>.
</p></ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
Attribute: document_identifier_assignment.assigned_group
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Specification_document_mim.document_identifier_assignment.assigned_group">
<p>
specifies a role of the <express_ref linkend="specification_document:mim:Specification_document_mim.document_identifier"/> for the <b>document_identifier_assignment</b>.
</p></ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
Entity: specification_definition
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Specification_document_mim.specification_definition">
<p>
An <b>specification_definition</b> is a type of <express_ref linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_definition"/> which implements the ARM concepts of:
</p><ul>
<li> <express_ref linkend="Assembly_technology:arm:Assembly_technology_arm.Assembly_technology_specification"/>;</li>
<li> <express_ref linkend="Specification_document:arm:Specification_document_arm.Design_specification"/>;</li>
<li> <express_ref linkend="Specification_document:arm:Specification_document_arm.Specification_definition"/>;</li>
<li> <express_ref linkend="Specification_document:arm:Specification_document_arm.Fabrication_technology_specification"/>;</li>
<li> <express_ref linkend="Specification_document:arm:Specification_document_arm.Interface_specification_document_definition"/>;</li>
<li> <express_ref linkend="Specification_document:arm:Specification_document_arm.Language_reference_manual"/>;</li>
<li> <express_ref linkend="Specification_document:arm:Specification_document_arm.Material_specification"/>;</li>
<li> <express_ref linkend="Specification_document:arm:Specification_document_arm.Process_specification"/>;</li>
<li> <express_ref linkend="Specification_document:arm:Specification_document_arm.Surface_finish_specification"/>;</li>
<li> <express_ref linkend="Specification_document:arm:Specification_document_arm.Test_specification"/>.</li>
</ul>
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
WR: specification_definition.WR1
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Specification_document_mim.specification_definition.wr:WR1">
The <b>specification_definition</b> shall have at least one organization or 
 <express_ref linkend="person_organization_schema:ir_express:person_organization_schema.person_and_organization"/> specified as its 'document source'.
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
WR: specification_definition.WR2
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Specification_document_mim.specification_definition.wr:WR2">
The <b>specification_definition</b> shall be a <express_ref linkend="Assembly_technology:arm:Assembly_technology_arm.Assembly_technology_specification"/>, <express_ref linkend="Specification_document:arm:Specification_document_arm.Design_specification"/>,
<express_ref linkend="Specification_document:arm:Specification_document_arm.Fabrication_technology_specification"/>,  <express_ref linkend="Specification_document:arm:Specification_document_arm.Interface_specification"/>,
<express_ref linkend="Specification_document:arm:Specification_document_arm.Language_reference_manual"/>, <express_ref linkend="Specification_document:arm:Specification_document_arm.Material_specification"/>,
reference document, font registration document,
source code, <express_ref linkend="Specification_document:arm:Specification_document_arm.Process_specification"/>, <express_ref linkend="Specification_document:arm:Specification_document_arm.Surface_finish_specification"/>, or a <express_ref linkend="Specification_document:arm:Specification_document_arm.Test_specification"/>.
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
Entity: structured_text_representation_context
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Specification_document_mim.structured_text_representation_context">
<p>
A <b>structured_text_representation_context</b> is a type of <express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.representation_context"/>  that implements the ARM concept of <express_ref linkend="Specification_document:mim:Specification_document_mim.structured_text_representation_item"/>.
</p></ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
WR: structured_text_representation_context.WR1
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Specification_document_mim.structured_text_representation_context.wr:WR1">
The <b>structured_text_representation_context</b> shall only be a context for representations that contain <express_ref linkend="Specification_document:mim:Specification_document_mim.structured_text_representation_item">structured_text_representation_items</express_ref>.
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
Entity: structured_text_representation_item
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Specification_document_mim.structured_text_representation_item">
<p>
A <b>structured_text_representation_item</b> is a type of <express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.representation"/>  and a  <express_ref linkend="qualified_measure_schema:ir_express:qualified_measure_schema.descriptive_representation_item"/>
that implements the ARM concept of <express_ref linkend="Specification_document:mim:Specification_document_mim.structured_text_representation_item"/>.
</p></ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
WR: structured_text_representation_item.WR1
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Specification_document_mim.structured_text_representation_item.wr:WR1">
The <b>structured_text_representation_item</b> shall relate to at most one <b>structured_text_representation_item</b> through a  <express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.representation_relationship"/>. 
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
WR: structured_text_representation_item.WR2
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Specification_document_mim.structured_text_representation_item.wr:WR2">
The <b>structured_text_representation_item</b> shall be referenced by at least one document.
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
WR: structured_text_representation_item.WR3
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Specification_document_mim.structured_text_representation_item.wr:WR3">
The <b>structured_text_representation_item</b> shall contain exactly one <express_ref linkend="External_item_identification_assignment:mim:External_item_identification_assignment_mim.applied_external_identification_assignment"/>.
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
Type: document_identifier_assigned_item
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Specification_document_mim.document_identifier_assigned_item">
A <b>document_identifier_assigned_item</b> type specifies those items
to which a  <express_ref linkend="Specification_document:mim:Specification_document_mim.document_identifier"/> may be assigned.
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
Rule: ee_document_constraint
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Specification_document_mim.ee_document_constraint">
The <b>ee_document_constraint</b> rule constrains the usage of a document.
</ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Specification_document_mim.ee_document_constraint.wr:WR1">
A document shall be an items of an <express_ref linkend="date_time_assignment:mim:Date_time_assignment_mim.applied_date_and_time_assignment"/> where the date and time is in the role of 'creation date'.
</ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Specification_document_mim.ee_document_constraint.wr:WR2">
A document shall be an items of 
(an <express_ref linkend="person_organization_assignment:mim:Person_organization_assignment_mim.applied_organization_assignment"/>.role.name = 'publisher') 
(a <express_ref linkend="person_organization_assignment:mim:Person_organization_assignment_mim.applied_person_and_organization_assignment"/>.role.name = 'publisher').
</ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Specification_document_mim.ee_document_constraint.wr:WR3">
A document shall be an items of exactly one <express_ref linkend="Specification_document:mim:Specification_document_mim.document_identifier_assignment"/>.
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
Rule: ee_document_unique_constraint
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Specification_document_mim.ee_document_unique_constraint">
The <b>ee_document_unique_constraint</b> rule constrains document population members, that fill the role of ARM <express_ref linkend="Document_definition:arm:Document_definition_arm.Document_definition"/>, so that ARM identification attributes shall be unique within the population.
The combination of <express_ref linkend="Product_view_definition:arm:Product_view_definition_arm.Product_view_definition.id"/> and <express_ref linkend="Document_definition:arm:Document_definition_arm.Document_definition.associated_document_version"/> shall be unique.
</ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Specification_document_mim.ee_document_unique_constraint.wr:WR1">
Every instance of document must have a unique combination of <express_ref linkend="Specification_document:mim:Specification_document_mim.document_identifier"/> and document.description.
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
Rule: product_association_constraint
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Specification_document_mim.product_association_constraint">
The <b>product_association_constraint</b> rule constrains the usage of a
<express_ref linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_definition_formation_relationship"/> when it is a product association.
</ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Specification_document_mim.product_association_constraint.wr:WR1">
IF <express_ref linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_definition_formation_relationship"/>.name = 'product association' 
THEN SELF shall be an items of an <express_ref linkend="document_assignment:mim:Document_assignment_mim.applied_document_reference"/> whose <express_ref linkend="management_resources_schema:ir_express:management_resources_schema.document_reference.assigned_document"/> is an <express_ref linkend="Specification_document:mim:Specification_document_mim.specification_definition"/>.
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
Rule: product_association_constraint
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Specification_document_mim.product_association_unique_constraint">
The <b>product_association_unique_constraint</b> rule constrains <express_ref linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_definition_formation_relationship"/>
population members, that fill the role of ARM <express_ref linkend="Product_version_relationship:arm:Product_version_relationship_arm.Product_version_relationship"/>.
</ext_description>
<ext_description linkend="Specification_document_mim.product_association_unique_constraint.wr:WR1">
Every instance of <express_ref linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_definition_formation_relationship"/> with a name of 'product
association' that has a common <express_ref linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_definition_formation_relationship.relating_product_definition_formation"/> must have
unique <express_ref linkend="Specification_document:mim:Specification_document_mim.specification_definition"/> entities assigned to the <express_ref linkend="product_definition_schema:ir_express:product_definition_schema.product_definition_formation_relationship"/>
by an <express_ref linkend="document_assignment:mim:Document_assignment_mim.applied_document_reference"/>'s items attribute.
</ext_description>

</ext_descriptions>
